    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it's really not that much just one glass. i've heard people say it makes the meds way more effective so you don't need as much of them. since i'm already feeling a little relaxed from the wine, wouldn't it just help me fall asleep quicker without being a big deal?",
